Tasks
The Group's tasks are the following:
(a) to establish cooperation between Member States' authorities and the Commission on questions relating to the recognition of professional qualifications;
(b) to monitor the evolution of policies having an impact on professions regulated as to qualifications;
(c) to facilitate the implementation of Directive 2005/36/EC, in particular through the elaboration of documents of interest, such as interpreting guidelines;
(d) to bring about an exchange of experience and good practice in the fields referred to in the previous points.
